The paper focuses on developing citation recommendation approaches using embeddings, topic modeling, and information retrieval techniques. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), deep learning (cs.DL), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
